government partners to identify emerging technologies and develop plans to synchronize investment
opportunities where applicable to share costs and avoid duplicative work.

- Conducted Multi-Service Advanced Capabilities for Hypersonics Test Bed (MACH-TB) testing to mature
advanced TPS manufacturing capabilities and operability testing for an advanced capability in transition to the
