Corps Aviation's Project Eagle, progressing these concepts through development, demonstration and ultimately transition into fieldable capabilities This PE funds
development of USMC Vertical Take-Off and Landing (VTOL) capabilities, including manned and unmanned air vehicles, and associated and requisite capabilities.
