to the FMF. Leveraging both government and commercial off-the-shelf solutions, as well as developmental items, MCRCO plays a critical role in maintaining the Marine
Corps' strategic readiness and technological edge.

 Additional details about the MCRCO, including project specifics, can be found at a higher classification level.

