and deter capabilities to integrate into the C-sUAS FoS. As the JCO designated CORIAN Acquisition Lead,
continue development, implementation and integration of additional sensor modalities to improve system detect/
ID/track/defeat capabilities. Continue efforts to improve interoperability between ashore and afloat C-sUAS
systems. Funding provides for continued development of data fusion architecture for external sensor integration




