       Change Summary Explanation
       Technical: Not Applicable

       Cost: FY27 increase of $29.083 million due to funding realignment from APN to RDTEN to support Growler Block II Phase II Beowulf.

       Schedule:

       Systems Development:
       Growler Block 2 / REAM Development efforts complete 1QFY26. Development efforts have been broken out to delineate the Growler Block 2 Phase 1
       (NGEAU) and Growler Block 2 Phase 2 (Beowulf) hardware and software phases. Growler Block 2 Development/NGEAU Hardware began Q1FY25 and ends
       Q2FY26. Growler Block 2 Development/NGEAU Software began Q1FY25. Growler Block 2 Development/Beowulf Hardware begins Q2FY26. Growler Block 2
       Development/Beowulf Software begins Q1FY26. Flight Plan Development / BLOS, Flight Plan Modeling and Simulation, and Flight Plan Studies and Analysis
       efforts end Q4FY25. Combined Flight Plan efforts begin Q1FY26.

       Test and Evaluation:
       Flight Plan Test and Evaluation efforts continues through 4QFY31. Test efforts have been broken out to delineate the Growler Block 2 Phase 1 (NGEAU) and
