in support of the penetrating jammer mission with plans to release variants of the AN/ALQ-231(V) BLK X Radar
Jammer for use on the MV-22 and KC-130J, as well as for future use on other USMC fixed wing, rotary wing,
and unmanned aircraft, as well as (V)3 Blk2 variant to provide additional capability to the Fleet.

